---
import background from '../assets/background.svg';
import alexProfessionalPic from '../assets/alexxu_profile.jpeg'
import smokeAppPic from '../assets/smoke-app-cover.png'
import btpHubLogo from '../assets/BTPHub_Logo.svg'
import fblaPic from '../assets/fbla-cover-photo.png'
---

<div id="container">
	<img id="background" src={background.src} alt="" fetchpriority="high" />
	<header class="header-container">
		<div class="logo">
			<div>
				<span style="font-size: 26px; color: #f5fcf5">
					<i class="fa-solid fa-code"></i>
				</span>
			</div>
			<div class="logo-name">
				Alexander Xu
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="nav-bar">
			<a href="#" class="nav-link">Home</a>
			<a href="#portfolio" class="nav-link">Project Portfolio</a>
			<a href="#" class="nav-link">About Me</a>
		</div>
	</header>
	
	<main>
		<div class="hero">
			<div class="hero-side-1">
				<div class="big-text">
					<span style="color: #ca36ff">Hi</span>, my name is Alexander Xu
				</div>
				<div class="basic-description">
					I am a junior at Johns Creek High School in Johns Creek, GA., a lover of math and STEM, an avid reader and writer, and a growing entrepreneur. 
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="hero-side-2">
				<img src={alexProfessionalPic.src} alt="" class="prof-pic" />
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="my-interests">
			<div class="interest-title">
				My Interests
			</div>
			<div class="interests-container">
				<div class="interest">
					<span class="interest-icon">
						Mathematics
					</span>
				</div>
				<div class="interest">
					<span class="interest-icon">
						Public Speaking
					</span>
				</div>
				<div class="interest">
					<span class="interest-icon">
						Computer Science
					</span>
				</div>
				<div class="interest">
					<span class="interest-icon">
						Creative Writing
					</span>
				</div>
				<div class="interest">
					<span class="interest-icon">
						Climate Advocacy
					</span>
				</div>
				<div class="interest">
					<span class="interest-icon">
						Student Research
					</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="portfolio" id="portfolio">
			<div class="portfolio-title">
				<div>
					My Project Portfolio
				</div>
				<div class="fancy-underline">
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="project-portfolio-container">

				<div class="portfolio-project">
					<div class="project-text">
						<div class="project-title">
							Smoke Aware: A Wildfire & Smoke Data App 
						</div>
						<div class="project-subtitle">
							<span style="color: red">
								<i class="fa-brands fa-youtube"></i>
							</span>
							Please watch the <b>demo video</b> (Congressional App Challenge GA-07 2nd Place Winner): 
							<a href="https://youtu.be/-WQ2pu42kxY" target="_blank"><b>Video</b></a>. 
						</div>
						<div class="project-subtitle">
							<span>
								<i class="fa-brands fa-github"></i>
							</span>
							Github: 
							<a href="https://github.com/AlexZXu/smoke-aware-congress-app" target="_blank"><b>Repo</b></a>
						</div>
						
						<div class="project-paragraph" style="margin-top: 15px">
							During my research with Emory Rollins School of Public Health on wildfire smoke, I saw how there were often challenges in accessing high quality data from sources like the government. 
							This data is critical for research analysis and creating prediction models. 
							I have always been concerned about climate change, and I am currently pushing a resolution for Fulton County Schools to reduce their climate impact through electrification and awareness. 
							This inspired me to create Smoke Aware.
						</div>
						<div class="project-paragraph">
							Key Features:
							<ul>
								<li>
									Data Visualization: Offers clear, user-friendly displays of real-time and historical smoke data, enabling users to explore trends with toggles, tooltips, and interactive graphs.
								</li>
								<li>
									Localized Forecasts: Allows users to input their zip code for personalized air quality insights and detailed hourly predictions.
								</li>
								<li>
									Custom Data Retrieval: Provides customizable tools to fetch, preview, and download datasets, supporting researchers with detailed analysis needs.
								</li>
								<li>
									AI-Powered Insights: Includes a custom AI model for answering wildfire and climate-related queries, enhancing efficiency for researchers and raising public awareness.
								</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="project-image">
						<img src={smokeAppPic.src} alt="" class="project-pic" />
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="portfolio-project">
					<div class="project-text">
						<div class="project-title">
							BTPHub: A Startup and App
						</div>
						<div class="project-subtitle">
							<span>
								<i class="fa-brands fa-figma"></i>
							</span>
							Pilot coming soon, see our app designs: 
							<a href="https://www.figma.com/design/31a6menUijKP9jhCsJEpi7/BTPHub-Master-Design-File?node-id=0-1&t=85VG4nGdyKUoNP1J-1" target="_blank"><b>Design File</b></a>
						</div>
						
						<div class="project-paragraph" style="margin-top: 15px">
							BTPHub is a tech startup focused on connecting families with trusted childcare and senior care providers within their local communities. 
							Our application makes it easy to find and schedule care, fostering stronger neighborhood connections.
							The app enables providers, such as babysitters and petsitters, to share their availability and accept service requests, while customers can easily find trusted providers nearby and manage all their bookings. 
							The app’s neighborhood-centered design ensures a trusted, community-based experience for all users.
						</div>
						<div class="project-paragraph">
							As the technical lead, our team uses tools like SQL databases, APIs, and JavaScript frameworks (e.g., Vue) to create a smooth and reliable user experience. 
							BTPHub aims to make care more accessible and convenient for everyone.
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="project-image" >
						<img src={btpHubLogo.src} alt="" class="project-pic" style="background: white" />
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="portfolio-project">
					<div class="project-text">
						<div class="project-title">
							BNT and BNT Foundation Website
						</div>
						<div class="project-subtitle">
							<span>
								<i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass"></i>
							</span>
							
						</div>
						<div class="project-subtitle">
							<span>
								<i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass"></i>
							</span>
							Visit demo smoothie shop website submitted for FBLA (2022 Regional 3rd Place in Web Design): 
							<a href="https://alex-fbla-app.vercel.app/" target="_blank"><b>Website</b></a>
						</div>
						
						<div class="project-paragraph" style="margin-top: 15px">
							BTPHub is a tech startup focused on connecting families with trusted childcare and senior care providers within their local communities. 
							Our application makes it easy to find and schedule care, fostering stronger neighborhood connections.
							The app enables providers, such as babysitters and petsitters, to share their availability and accept service requests, while customers can easily find trusted providers nearby and manage all their bookings. 
							The app’s neighborhood-centered design ensures a trusted, community-based experience for all users.
						</div>
						<div class="project-paragraph">
							As the technical lead, our team uses tools like SQL databases, APIs, and JavaScript frameworks (e.g., Vue) to create a smooth and reliable user experience. 
							BTPHub aims to make care more accessible and convenient for everyone.
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="project-image" >
						<img src={fblaPic.src} alt="" class="project-pic" style="background: white" />
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</main>
</div>

<style>
	* {
		box-sizing: border-box;
	}
	#background {
		position: fixed;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		width: 100vw;
		height: 100vh;
		z-index: -1;
		filter: blur(100px);
	}

	#container {
		font-family: Inter, Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', 'Arial Nova', 'Nimbus Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
		height: 100%;
		width: 100%;
	}

	main {
		padding-top: 70px;
		height: fit-content;
		width: 100%;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;		
	}

	.header-container {
		position: fixed;
		top: 0;
		width: 100%;
		max-width: 100vw;
		align-items: center;
		height: 70px;
		background: rgb(38, 38, 38);
		display: flex;
	}

	.logo {
		position: absolute;
		display: flex;
		left: 25px;
		gap: 16px;
		align-items: center;
		color: #f5fcf5;
		font-weight: 500;
		font-size: 22px;
		font-family: 'Rubik', sans-serif;
		letter-spacing: 0.01cm;
		font-stretch: expanded;
	}

	.nav-bar {
		color: white;
		display: flex;
		margin: auto;
		border: solid 1px white;
		border-radius: 1000px;
		padding: 10px;
		padding-left: 20px;
		padding-right: 20px;
		background: rgb(38, 38, 38);
		gap: 30px;
	}

	.nav-link {
		color: #fdfdfd;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 600;
		transition: color 0.2s;
	}
	
	.nav-link:hover {
		color: #ffe0f9;
	}

	.hero {
		margin-top: 25px;
		margin-bottom: 40px;
		max-width: 1320px;
		height: 550px;
		width: 85%;
		display: flex;
		gap: 35px;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.hero-side-1 {
		flex: 1;
	}
	.big-text {
		font-family: 'Rubik', sans-serif;
		font-size: 64px;
		font-weight: 500;
		color: rgb(38, 38, 38);
		text-shadow: 0px 0px 15px #f1cbf1;
	}

	.basic-description {
		font-family: 'Rubik', sans-serif;
		margin-top: 20px;
		color: rgb(71, 68, 68);
		line-height: 30px;
		font-size: 22px;
		font-weight: 4500;
		width: 90%;
	}

	.hero-side-2 {
		width: 40%;
		height: 100%;
	}

	.prof-pic {
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		object-fit: cover;
		border-radius: 60px;
		box-shadow: rgba(100, 100, 111, 0.2) 0px 7px 29px 0px;
	}

	.my-interests {
		border-top: 2px solid rgb(96, 96, 96);
		border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(96, 96, 96);
		padding-top: 25px;
		padding-bottom: 25px;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		width: 100%;
	}

	.interest-title {
		font-size: 24px;
		font-weight: 600;
		font-family: 'Inter';
		margin-bottom: 12px;
	}

	.fancy-underline {
		background: rgb(216,109,195);
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(216,109,195,1) 0%, rgba(255,112,112,1) 100%);
		height: 5px;
		width: 100%;
	}

	.interests-container {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 12px;
		justify-content: center;
		width: 80%;
	}
	
	.interest {
		border: solid;
		padding: 5px;
		padding-left: 15px;
		padding-right: 15px;
		border-radius: 20px;
	}

	.portfolio {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		width: 100%;
		gap: 30px;
		padding-top: 40px;
		padding-bottom: 30px;
	}

	.portfolio-title {
		font-weight: 600;
		font-size: 42px;
	}

	.project-portfolio-container {
		max-width: 1320px;
		width: 85%;
		gap: 30px;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
	}

	.portfolio-project {
		display: flex;
		height: 400px;
		width: 100%;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.744);
		padding: 25px;
		border-radius: 16px;
		gap: 15px;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
	}

	.project-text {
		width: 60%;
		border: rgb(183, 178, 178) 1px solid;
		border-radius: 10px;
		padding: 16px;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 10px;
		overflow-y: auto;
	}

	.project-title {
		font-size: 34px;
		font-weight: 600;
		padding-bottom: 7px;
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(116, 113, 113);
	}
	
	.project-subtitle {
		font-size: 20px;
		color: black;
	}

	.project-paragraph {
		font-weight: 300;
		font-size: 16px;
	}

	.project-image {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 10px;
		width: 40%;
	}

	.project-pic {
		object-fit: cover;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		border-radius: 20px;
		box-shadow: rgba(100, 100, 111, 0.104) 0px 2px 15px 0px;
	}
</style>
